'''Hijarna stone''' was a material found in a [[Fortress of Hijarna|fortress]] on [[Hijarna]], as well as the [[Hand of Thrawn]] on [[Nirauan/Legends|Nirauan]]. A safe belonging to crime lord Avrak Villachor was also made of Hijarna stone. The stone was black, incredibly dense, and had the apparent ability to absorb laser or [[Turbolaser/Legends|turbolaser]] fire like a sponge. This is not to say it was invulnerable to all forms of energy attacks, however - a powerful enough laser blast, such as that from a [[Superlaser/Legends|superlaser]], would damage it. Additionally, it could absorb energy somewhat from lightsabers but after enough hits the stone would break.

